=== EVENT_MEDITATION_NEBULA ===
# id: 72
# title: Meditation Nebula
# chinese_title: 冥想星云
# category: LanguageChallenge
# mode: starmap

A serene nebula emits frequencies that enhance mental clarity. Ancient travelers left language puzzles carved into floating monoliths as tests of wisdom.

* [[Gain radical 言] Solve the word puzzle on the first monolith]
  ~ gain_radical("言")
  言 (yán) — speech, word
* [[Gain radical 竹] Decode the nature cipher on the second]
  ~ gain_radical("竹")
  竹 (zhú) — bamboo
* [[Heal 5 HP] Meditate in the calming frequencies]
  ~ heal_crew(5)
  静 (jìng) — calm
* [[+20 credits] Photograph and sell the inscriptions]
  ~ gain_credits(20)
  照 (zhào) — photograph
* [[-5 fuel, Gain radical 页] Follow the monolith trail deeper] {requires: fuel >= 5}
  ~ gain_radical("页")
  页 (yè) — page
